at a face to calm my fear.

584
00:29:06,014 --> 00:29:06,813
Then,

585
00:29:09,313 --> 00:29:10,774
how do I compare to him?

586
00:29:15,254 --> 00:29:16,133
In my heart,

587
00:29:16,133 --> 00:29:17,673
Lord Marquis is a
noble gentleman,

588
00:29:17,754 --> 00:29:18,413
unmatched by anyone.

589
00:29:59,573 --> 00:30:00,054
Sir,

590
00:30:00,534 --> 00:30:01,474
without proper permission,

591
00:30:01,813 --> 00:30:02,573
you cannot enter.

592
00:30:03,813 --> 00:30:05,474
Commander An, why
don’t you wait outside?

593
00:30:05,813 --> 00:30:07,393
Miss Jiang and I will go inside.

594
00:30:14,093 --> 00:30:15,254
Just now, in the carriage,

595
00:30:15,454 --> 00:30:16,754
you reacted quickly.

596
00:30:17,893 --> 00:30:19,054
If it weren’t for you,

597
00:30:19,313 --> 00:30:20,994
I wouldn’t have to
sneak around like this.

598
00:30:22,054 --> 00:30:23,073
Who was sneaking around

599
00:30:23,073 --> 00:30:24,333
to slip into Fanglin Garden?

600
