714
00:34:54,133 --> 00:34:55,494
He quickly pulled me away.

715
00:35:02,874 --> 00:35:03,974
If you’re going to
interrogate Fan Yi,

716
00:35:04,633 --> 00:35:05,213
I’m coming too.

717
00:35:06,733 --> 00:35:08,054
That’s not quite
appropriate, is it?

718
00:35:08,814 --> 00:35:10,113
If you don’t let me come,

719
00:35:10,293 --> 00:35:11,514
I’ll go back and tell
the Lord Marquis!

720
00:35:11,514 --> 00:35:12,894
Fan Yi was your planted man.

721
00:35:14,733 --> 00:35:15,414
What’s wrong?

722
00:35:15,793 --> 00:35:16,854
Afraid to take me with you?

723
00:35:19,793 --> 00:35:21,573
You’ve certainly
learned to act the part.

724
00:35:31,894 --> 00:35:32,534
Commander Wei,

725
00:35:32,874 --> 00:35:33,573
