781
00:37:14,394 --> 00:37:14,773
No!

782
00:37:15,193 --> 00:37:16,293
I didn’t collude
with any assassin!

783
00:37:18,593 --> 00:37:19,073
Commander Wei,

784
00:37:20,054 --> 00:37:21,593
for the sake of our
years of service together,

785
00:37:21,854 --> 00:37:23,494
both serving His Majesty,

786
00:37:23,773 --> 00:37:24,414
I beg you,

787
