795
00:37:43,133 --> 00:37:43,554
Yes.

796
00:37:44,073 --> 00:37:44,753
It was very windy.

797
00:37:45,394 --> 00:37:46,054
Deputy General Tong and I

798
00:37:46,054 --> 00:37:47,394
patrolled behind the house,

799
00:37:47,394 --> 00:37:48,293
