813
00:38:15,133 --> 00:38:16,133
I’ll accompany you.

814
00:38:16,954 --> 00:38:17,733
Then...

815
00:38:18,293 --> 00:38:19,534
Commander Wei?

816
00:38:20,414 --> 00:38:20,954
It’s fine.

817
00:38:21,693 --> 00:38:23,133
Since I promised
the Lord Marquis

