00:38:41,733 --> 00:38:43,573
Take them home, plant them, and
they'll bloom into beautiful flowers.

823
00:38:43,713 --> 00:38:44,633
I’ll take this one.

824
00:38:45,834 --> 00:38:46,173
Here.

825
00:38:46,874 --> 00:38:48,073
Alright, it's packed for you.

826
00:38:48,733 --> 00:38:50,014
The vegetable
market is just ahead.

827
00:38:50,073 --> 00:38:51,054
Let’s go have a look.

828
00:38:51,054 --> 00:38:51,713
Fresh flowers for sale!

829
00:38:51,854 --> 00:38:52,713
Flower seeds!

830
00:38:54,273 --> 00:38:55,213
Come, look at my fresh flowers.

831
00:38:55,213 --> 00:38:56,474
Brother, give me some money.

832
00:38:56,474 --> 00:38:57,854
Give me some money, brother.

833
00:38:58,073 --> 00:38:59,253
Go ask the man in the purple.

834
00:39:00,034 --> 00:39:01,334
Ask that brother up ahead.

835
00:39:02,334 --> 00:39:07,034
Brother, give me some money.

836
00:39:08,454 --> 00:39:10,293
Please, give some, brother.

837
00:39:15,994 --> 00:39:17,773
You’re not planning to do
anything to An Cheng, are you?

838
00:39:18,153 --> 00:39:19,073
I’m not foolish enough

839
00:39:19,073 --> 00:39:21,293
to commit a crime in
broad daylight on the street.

840
00:39:22,914 --> 00:39:23,354
Now, talk.

841
00:39:24,073 --> 00:39:24,793
What do you want from me?

842
00:39:26,494 --> 00:39:27,633
You’re from Moonfall City.

843
00:39:29,014 --> 00:39:29,854
Moonfall City?

844
00:39:30,253 --> 00:39:32,173
That day, I made a bowl
of "Not Bitter Porridge."

845
00:39:32,514 --> 00:39:34,394
You were the only one who
noticed the taste was different.

846
00:39:34,914 --> 00:39:35,914
I just said

847
00:39:36,213 --> 00:39:37,514
I don’t like sweet things.

848
00:39:37,854 --> 00:39:39,854
You said it was too sweet.

849
00:39:40,193 --> 00:39:41,233
And you agreed
with the Lord Marquis

850
00:39:41,233 --> 00:39:42,454
and Brother Cui.

851
00:39:43,054 --> 00:39:44,573
You said it was too sweet,

852
00:39:44,914 --> 00:39:46,293
but in fact, it
wasn’t bitter enough.

853
00:39:48,273 --> 00:39:48,834
Is that so?

854
00:39:49,394 --> 00:39:51,673
Not Bitter Porridge initially
tastes sweet and mellow.

855
00:39:52,073 --> 00:39:54,014
Then, a bitterness follows.

856
00:39:54,073 --> 00:39:55,173
The taste lingers sweetly.

857
00:39:55,494 --> 00:39:57,173
It has a unique flavor.

858
00:39:57,293 --> 00:39:58,434
It’s because there’s
a flower inside,

859
00:39:58,434 --> 00:40:00,374
a Lingjiu flower,
sweet yet bitter.

860
00:40:00,874 --> 00:40:02,793
This flower only
grows in Moonfall City.

861
00:40:02,914 --> 00:40:04,113
And "Not Bitter
Porridge" as well.

862
00:40:04,673 --> 00:40:05,733
In this world,

863
00:40:05,934 --> 00:40:07,054
those who know
"Not Bitter Porridge"

864
00:40:07,193 --> 00:40:09,073
and have tasted
its authentic flavor

865
00:40:09,334 --> 00:40:10,713
are few and far between.

866
00:40:12,054 --> 00:40:13,514
It’s just a bowl of porridge.

867
00:40:13,673 --> 00:40:14,914
But that day in the tree,

868
00:40:14,914 --> 00:40:16,773
you were ready to kill me,

869
00:40:17,014 --> 00:40:18,673
yet when you saw
the Moonfall Journal,

870
00:40:18,793 --> 00:40:19,773
you hesitated.

871
00:40:20,073 --> 00:40:21,593
Later, you even
casually mentioned

872
00:40:21,593 --> 00:40:23,014
Moonfall to me.

873
00:40:24,394 --> 00:40:25,054
And?

874
00:40:27,273 --> 00:40:28,253
Moonfall people

875
00:40:28,994 --> 00:40:30,613
are naturally handsome.

876
00:40:31,273 --> 00:40:32,113
Lian’er was,

877
00:40:33,153 --> 00:40:33,894
and so are you.

878
00:40:38,554 --> 00:40:39,354
So,

879
00:40:39,573 --> 00:40:40,753
you purposely said

880
00:40:41,213 --> 00:40:42,994
that the porridge
was your creation,

881
00:40:43,454 --> 00:40:44,633
waiting for me to expose you.

882
00:40:45,034 --> 00:40:45,974
I was gambling.

883
00:40:47,914 --> 00:40:48,554
Gambling on what?

884
00:40:48,713 --> 00:40:50,834
Gambling that you are a wanderer
without a home to return to.

885
00:40:51,753 --> 00:40:52,613
For wanderers,

886
00:40:52,613 --> 00:40:54,573
their homesickness
is hard to suppress.

887
00:40:55,374 --> 00:40:56,874
But you guard
your heart too well.

888
00:40:57,233 --> 00:40:59,273
It’s too hard to find any clues.

889
00:40:59,773 --> 00:41:00,434
So

890
00:41:00,434 --> 00:41:01,414
I had no choice but to use

891
00:41:01,414 --> 00:41:03,213
a dish from your
homeland to test you.

892
00:41:03,434 --> 00:41:04,914
Even if it just stirred

893
00:41:04,914 --> 00:41:06,434
a small flicker of
emotion, it was enough.

894
00:41:08,293 --> 00:41:09,093
Even if

895
00:41:10,273 --> 00:41:11,693
I am from Moonfall City,

896
00:41:11,934 --> 00:41:13,073
what can you do about it?

897
00:41:13,514 --> 00:41:15,354
Give me back my clay cat.

898
00:41:15,573 --> 00:41:16,773
Otherwise, I’ll tell
the Lord Marquis,

899
00:41:16,773 --> 00:41:17,994
and you won’t be able to escape.

900
00:41:18,514 --> 00:41:19,113
Really?

901
00:41:20,233 --> 00:41:21,454
If I told you that

902
00:41:21,653 --> 00:41:23,414
if anything happened to me,

903
00:41:23,673 --> 00:41:24,834
the people of Jiangjia Village

904
00:41:24,934 --> 00:41:26,073
would die with me,

905
00:41:26,693 --> 00:41:27,514
would you believe me?

906
00:41:31,173 --> 00:41:32,273
I hit the mark.

907
00:41:35,593 --> 00:41:37,854
Do you think you can
use them to threaten me?

908
00:41:38,193 --> 00:41:39,994
They’ve called me a wild
girl since I was a child.

909
00:41:40,193 --> 00:41:41,593
Always giving me cold looks,

910
00:41:41,593 --> 00:41:42,733
throwing stones at me.

911
00:41:42,733 --> 00:41:43,934
I hated them so much,

912
00:41:43,934 --> 00:41:45,713
why would I care
about their lives?

913
00:41:47,153 --> 00:41:49,133
But I’m an outsider anyway.

914
00:41:49,414 --> 00:41:50,073
It’s not worth it

915
00:41:50,073 --> 00:41:51,434
to have a full-blown
fight with you.

916
00:41:52,073 --> 00:41:52,454
Tell you what,

917
00:41:52,994 --> 00:41:54,494
just give me back my clay cat.

918
00:41:54,753 --> 00:41:55,653
I already told you,

919
00:41:55,914 --> 00:41:56,934
the mountain is hidden...

920
00:41:56,934 --> 00:41:57,773
The waters stretch far.

921
00:41:57,773 --> 00:41:59,414
I promise you, we
won’t meet again.

922
00:41:59,414 --> 00:42:00,693
And I won’t ruin
your plans anymore.

923
00:42:03,014 --> 00:42:03,793
Jiang Ci,

924
00:42:04,394 --> 00:42:06,054
it’s not that I’m purposely
making things difficult for you.

925
00:42:06,793 --> 00:42:08,573
We each serve our own masters.

926
00:42:08,733 --> 00:42:10,073
You have places you want to go,

927
00:42:10,153 --> 00:42:11,653
and I have things I want to do.

928
00:42:13,293 --> 00:42:14,474
You have a master?

929
00:42:15,514 --> 00:42:16,073
Who is it?

930
00:42:18,414 --> 00:42:19,994
He’s even more
ruthless than I am.

931
00:42:20,414 --> 00:42:21,693
It’s better if you don’t know.

932
00:42:23,474 --> 00:42:25,633
Is it the Xiao Wuxia
the Marquis mentioned?

933
00:42:27,494 --> 00:42:28,773
You’re not Xiao Wuxia.

934
00:42:29,673 --> 00:42:31,233
If you're so familiar
with "Not Bitter Porridge,"

935
00:42:31,514 --> 00:42:32,414
then you should know

936
00:42:33,093 --> 00:42:33,773
that "Not Bitter Porridge"

937
00:42:33,954 --> 00:42:35,593
is just a common street food.

938
00:42:36,093 --> 00:42:38,054
Xiao Wuxia is the young
master of Moonfall City.

939
00:42:38,554 --> 00:42:40,054
How could he be
wandering the streets,

940
00:42:40,193 --> 00:42:41,793
eating something so lowly?

941
00:42:42,454 --> 00:42:43,974
And how could a bowl of porridge

942
00:42:44,153 --> 00:42:45,573
stir up his homesickness?

943
00:42:47,354 --> 00:42:48,954
Was the one who broke
into the courtyard that night

944
00:42:48,954 --> 00:42:49,773
him?

945
00:42:51,173 --> 00:42:52,054
Questions you shouldn’t ask,

946
00:42:52,054 --> 00:42:53,073
you shouldn’t ask.

947
00:42:53,673 --> 00:42:54,874
All I can tell you

948
00:42:55,514 --> 00:42:56,753
is that I never went
to the courtyard,

949
00:42:57,273 --> 00:42:58,213
and I never killed anyone.

950
00:42:58,914 --> 00:43:01,054
But the Marquis
will still suspect you.

951
00:43:01,514 --> 00:43:02,773
As long as Pei Yan believes you,

952
00:43:03,193 --> 00:43:04,113
he will believe me.

953
00:43:05,914 --> 00:43:06,733
What do you mean?

954
00:43:07,494 --> 00:43:08,773
As long as Pei Yan believes

955
00:43:09,354 --> 00:43:11,034
you won’t betray or deceive him,

956
00:43:11,633 --> 00:43:12,693
then my actions,

957
00:43:12,693 --> 00:43:13,954
which are naturally
linked to you,

958
00:43:14,293 --> 00:43:15,914
will not be questioned either.

959
00:43:16,994 --> 00:43:18,173
But in my view,

960
00:43:18,753 --> 00:43:19,434
Miss Jiang,

961
00:43:19,753 --> 00:43:21,673
you probably wouldn’t want
to deceive him anymore.

962
00:43:26,293 --> 00:43:28,394
As long as the Marquis
no longer suspects you,

963
00:43:28,894 --> 00:43:30,593
you'll return my clay cat to me.

964
00:43:32,414 --> 00:43:32,974
Of course.

965
00:43:34,593 --> 00:43:35,034
Alright.

966
00:43:35,613 --> 00:43:36,514
It’s a deal.

967
00:43:37,954 --> 00:43:39,213
In the future, if you
have something to say

968
00:43:39,414 --> 00:43:40,394
but it’s inconvenient to speak,

969
00:43:41,054 --> 00:43:42,193
just make a signal
with the moon.

970
00:43:42,394 --> 00:43:43,073
When the time comes,

971
00:43:43,374 --> 00:43:44,534
I'll find a place

972
00:43:44,854 --> 00:43:45,593
to meet with you.

973
00:43:45,773 --> 00:43:48,014
Once I’m done
with this, we’re even.

974
00:43:48,014 --> 00:43:49,573
There’s nothing more to say.

975
00:43:51,093 --> 00:43:51,494
Alright.

976
00:44:09,773 --> 00:44:10,073
Here.

977
00:44:10,554 --> 00:44:11,173
No need for change.
Alright, alright, thank you.

978
00:44:11,394 --> 00:44:11,834
Thanks.

979
00:44:13,713 --> 00:44:15,334
Why did you pack me
all these vegetables?

980
00:44:16,093 --> 00:44:17,894
The person spying
on us has returned.

981
00:44:21,014 --> 00:44:22,034
Commander An.

982
00:44:22,093 --> 00:44:23,494
When did he start following us?

983
00:44:24,054 --> 00:44:25,914
As long as Pei Yan
hasn’t been dealt with,

984
00:44:25,914 --> 00:44:26,874
this situation

985
00:44:26,914 --> 00:44:28,073
is likely to repeat many times.

986
00:44:29,994 --> 00:44:30,874
But that’s fine.

987
00:44:31,394 --> 00:44:32,573
If An Cheng reports back,

988
00:44:32,914 --> 00:44:33,793
Pei Yan will trust it more.

989
00:44:40,054 --> 00:44:40,854
What are you doing?

990
00:44:41,273 --> 00:44:42,994
You still don’t
understand a man’s heart.

